<br>
I often see on these forums people mentioning that sometimes a tank can have trouble getting agro back off another player for example a cleric throwing around Complete Heals.<br>
<br>
How can this be because whenever you talk to a melee character they get annoyed by &quot;taunt bashers&quot; and explain again and again that you just have to time taunting correctly because hitting the taunt button gives you the aggro of the player in the group with highest aggro +1.<br>
<br>
If this is the case surely the tank should never lose aggro.<br>
<br>
Just curious... <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=jadrax>Jadrax</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Arcanist</span><br>  Posts: 1473<br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/26/03 5:16 am)</font><br>     <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> ah</span><hr size=1> The taunt skill only has a % chance of working.<br>
<br>
The best thing about AE taunt AA is it always taunts, but sadly its on a long reuse timer. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=azzitay>Azzitay</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Evoker</span><br>  Posts: 363<br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/26/03 8:04 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ah</span><hr size=1> That % chance is why most Tanks just Spam the Button ...<br>
