<br>
Thats why you as Wuzzard should have Concussion ... in case of Aggro channel through it and the Mob wanders back =) <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center">Master Azzitay Flammenpfad, Ratsmitglied <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.der-schatten.com" target="top">Der Schatten</a><!--EZCODE LINK END-->,</div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center">Sage Chimaeron Emrys, Member of Wind of Tranquility</div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=hibashira>Hibashira</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Evoker</span><br>  Posts: 489<br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/26/03 11:12 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ah</span><hr size=1> Taunt also has recycle time.  Until it is available again, tank can't use taunt. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=328193"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.geocities.com/hibashirasakai/HibashiraNewHalfSize.txt"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=wandork>Wandor K</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Arcanist<BR>Warriors ph34r me!<BR>Gnomercy for Gno-one!</span><br>  Posts: 2231<br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/26/03 11:24 am)</font><br>     <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Aggro management</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>How can this be because whenever you talk to a melee character they get annoyed by &quot;taunt bashers&quot; and explain again and again that you just have to time taunting correctly because hitting the taunt button gives you the aggro of the player in the group with highest aggro +1.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
This is correct, taunt does give you highest agro +1 on a successful taunt. However, you have to keep a few things in mind.<br>
<br>
'Taunt bashers' suck. Taunt has a 6 second recycle so if your tank is mashing the taunt button every 6 seconds, its a waste if he already has top agro, plus now he stands the chance of losing agro and not having taunt ready.<br>
<br>
Taunt DOES NOT work on mobs that are higher level than the tank until level 60. Period. This is hard coded. Once a tank gets 60, they can taunt higher level mobs, but I believe there is a cap (+3 levels higher than tank I think it is), but keep in mind that the higher the mob level, the less likely taunt is to work.<br>
<br>
1 point of hate is nothing. Remember that the tank is very likely doing the least amount of damage so if the person who pulled agro is a damage dealer and they don't stop dealing damage, they will get agro right back. Same with healers, if the healer gets agro, then gets low HP agro, then gets additional heal agro, the tank is going to have a rough time getting agro back.<br>
<br>
Even with a pally or SK tanking, agro control is EVERYONE's job. It is up to you do the things that will help keep agro on the tank. That means using concussion/jolt, knowing how proximity effects agro, knowing where to stand when you know you are going to take agro (tash, slow, or on purpose to help cleric land a heal).<br>
